  <p>
    Meristem Woodworks is the home for the furniture and interior carpentry work of Philip Shelton. <br/>
    I characterize my furniture design style as wood-forward; showcasing the wood for what it is, without diminishing or masking it. <br/>
    The wood itself is the centerpiece and the aesthetic of my work.  
  </p>
